                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-599-18350202 t18350202-599-punishment-105"></join>Confined One Year</rs>.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Fifth Jury, before Mr. Sergeant Arabin</hi>.</p>
